  "raw_block": "Descended from Ham —Ge 10:6.\nAn accursed race —Ge 9:25,26.\nDifferent families of —Ge 10:15-18.\nComprised seven distinct nations —De 7:1.\nPossessions of, how bounded —Ge 10:19.\nCountry of, fertile —Ex 3:17;Nu 13:27.\nDescribed as\n  Great and mighty. —Nu 13:28;De 7:1.\n  Idolatrous. —De 29:17.\n  Superstitious. —De 18:9-11.\n  Profane and wicked. —Le 18:27.\nExtremely numerous —De 7:17.\nHad many strong cities —Nu 13:28;De 1:28.\nExpelled for wickedness —De 9:4;18:12.\nAbraham\n  Called to dwell amongst. —Ge 12:1-5.\n  Was promised the country of, of inheritance. —Ge 13:14-17;15:18;17:8.\n  Had his faith tried by dwelling amongst. —Ge 12:6;13:7.\nKind to the patriarchs —Ge 14:13;23:6.\nIsrael commanded\n  To make no league with. —De 7:2;Jdj 2:2.\n  Not to intermarry with. —De 7:3;Jos 23:12.\n  Not to follow idols of. —Ex 23:24;De 7:25.\n  Not to follow customs of. —Le 18:26,27.\n  To destroy, without mercy. —De 7:2,24.\n  To destroy all vestiges of their idolatry. —Ex 23:24;De 7:5,25.\n  Not to fear. —De 7:",
